-></div><script>(self.__next_s=self.__next_s||[]).push([\"https://sdk.mercadopago.com/js/v2\",{}])</script><main class=\"flex-1 w-full flex flex-col\"><style data-emotion=\"css 1eag56u\">.css-1eag56u{width:100%;margin-left:auto;box-sizing:border-box;margin-right:auto;display:block;padding-left:16px;padding-right:16px;padding-top:48px;padding-bottom:48px;}@media (min-width:600px){.css-1eag56u{padding-left:24px;padding-right:24px;}}@media (min-width:900px){.css-1eag56u{max-width:900px;}}</style><div class=\"MuiContainer-root MuiContainer-maxWidthMd css-1eag56u\"><style data-emotion=\"css 1nwmaq7\">.css-1nwmaq7{margin:0;font-family:Inter,sans-serif;font-weight:400;font-size:3rem;line-height:1.167;margin-bottom:0.35em;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:32px;}</style><h3 class=\"MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-h3 MuiTypography-gutterBottom css-1nwmaq7\">Política de Troca e Cancelamento</h3><style data-emotion=\"css 1i43dhb\">.css-1i43dhb{display:-webkit-box;display:-webkit-flex;display:-ms-flexbox;display:flex;-webkit-flex-direction:column;-ms-flex-direction:column;flex-direction:column;gap:24px;}</style><div class=\"MuiBox-root css-1i43dhb\"><div class=\"MuiBox-root css-0\"><style data-emotion=\"css iszxqw\">.css-iszxqw{margin:0;font-family:Inter,sans-serif;font-weight:400;font-size:1.5rem;line-height:1.334;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:16px;}</style><h5 class=\"MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-h5 css-iszxqw\">Cancelamento de Pedidos</h5><style data-emotion=\"css 1ivy3ri\">.css-1ivy3ri{margin:0;font-family:Inter,sans-serif;font-weight:400;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:16px;line-height:1.7;}</style><p class=\"MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-body1 css-1ivy3ri\">Você pode cancelar seu pedido em até <strong>24 horas</strong> após a confirmação da compra. Após este período, o pedido será processado e enviado ao fornecedor.</p><style data-emotion=\"css 17yxpxh\">.css-17yxpxh{margin:0;font-family:Inter,sans-serif;font-weight:400;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.5;line-height:1.7;}</style><p class=\"MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-body1 css-17yxpxh\">Para cancelar, entre em contato conosco através de nossa plataforma antes do prazo.</p></div><div class=\"MuiBox-root css-0\"><h5 class=\"MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-h5 css-iszxqw\">Trocas</h5><p class=\"MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-body1 css-1ivy3ri\">Aceitamos trocas de produtos em até <strong>30 dias</strong> após o recebimento, desde que:</p><style data-emotion=\"css iy1l79\">.css-iy1l79{padding-left:16px;margin-bottom:16px;}</style><ul class=\"MuiBox-root css-iy1l79\"><style data-emotion=\"css 11grm9d\">.css-11grm9d{margin:0;font-family:Inter,sans-serif;font-weight:400;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.5;margin-bottom:8px;}</style><li class=\"MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-body1 css-11grm9d\">O produto esteja em condições originais e não tenha sido utilizado</li><li class=\"MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-body1 css-11grm9d\">A embalagem original esteja íntegra</li><style data-emotion=\"css 19tcczm\">.css-19tcczm{margin:0;font-family:Inter,sans-serif;font-weight:400;font-size:1rem;line-height:1.5;}</style><li class=\"MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-body1 css-19tcczm\">Todos os acessórios e manuais estejam inclusos</li></ul></div><div class=\"MuiBox-root css-0\"><h5 class=\"MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-h5 css-iszxqw\">Devoluções</h5><p class=\"MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-body1 css-17yxpxh\">Para mais informações sobre devoluções, consulte nossa <strong>Política de Devolução</strong> completa.</p></div><div class=\"MuiBox-root css-0\"><h5 class=\"MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-h5 css-iszxqw\">Prazo de Processamento</h5><p class=\"MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-body1 css-1ivy3ri\">Após aprovação da troca ou cancelamento, o reembolso será processado em até <strong>7 dias úteis</strong>.</p></div><style data-emotion=\"css r4c0au\">.css-r4c0au{margin-top:32px;padding:16px;background-color:rgba(0,0,0,0.04);border-radius:8px;}</style><div class=\"MuiBox-root css-r4c0au\"><style data-emotion=\"css 9k6gje\">.css-9k6gje{margin:0;font-family:Inter,sans-serif;font-weight:400;font-size:0.875rem;line-height:1.43;color:#555555;line-height:1.8;}</style><p class=\"MuiTypography-root MuiTypography-body2 css-9k6gje\">Dúvidas? Entre em contato conosco. Estamos aqui para ajudar!</p></div></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main><style data-emotion=\"css z6g4oh\">.css-z6g4oh{padding-top:48px;padding-bottom:48px;border-top:1px solid #E3E8EF;background-color:#FFFFFF;color:#1A1A1A;}</style><footer class=\"MuiBox-root css-z6g4oh\"><style data-emotion=\"css 1qsxih2\">.css-1qsxih2{width:100%;margin-left:auto;box-sizing:border-box;margin-right:auto;display:block;padding-left:16px;padding-right:16px;}@media (min-width:600px){.css-1qsxih2{padding-left:24px;padding-right:24px;}}@media (min-width:1200px){.css-1qsxih2{max-width:1200px;}}</style><div class=\"MuiContainer-root MuiContainer-maxWidthLg css-1qsxih2\"><style data-emotion=\"css 1tz8m30\">.css-1tz8m30{box-sizing:border-box;display:-webkit-box;display:-webkit-flex;display:-ms-flexbox;display:flex;-webkit-box-flex-wrap:wrap;-webkit-flex-wrap:wrap;-ms-flex-wrap:wrap;flex-wrap:wrap;width:100%;-webkit-flex-direction:row;-ms-flex-direction:row;flex-direction:row;margin-top:-32px;width:calc(100% + 32px);margin-left:-32px;}.css-1tz8m30>.MuiGrid-item{padding-top:32px;}.css-1tz8m30>.MuiGrid-item{padding-left:32px;}</style><div class=\"MuiGrid-root MuiGrid-container MuiGrid-spacing-xs-4 css-1tz8m30\"><style data-emotion=\"css 1pmmlk2\">.css-1pmmlk2{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;-webkit-flex-direction:row;-ms-flex-direction:row;flex-direction:row;-webkit-flex-basis:100%;-ms-flex-preferred-size:100%;flex-basis:100%;-webkit-box-flex:0;-webkit-flex-grow:0;-ms-flex-positive:0;flex-grow:0;max-width:100%;}@media (min-width:600px){.css-1pmmlk2{-webkit-flex-basis:50%;-ms-flex-preferred-size:50%;flex-basis:50%;-webkit-box-flex:0;-webkit-flex-grow:0;-ms-flex-positive:0;flex-grow:0;max-width:50%;}}@media (min-width:900px)